@startuml
title Activity: Arrest Processing

start
:Observe Violation/Probable Cause;
:Stop & Identify Suspect;
if (Resistance?) then (Yes)
  :Use Appropriate Force;
else (No)
  :Proceed with Arrest;
endif
:Read Rights;
:Handcuff Suspect;
:Search Incident to Arrest;
:Transport to Station;
:Booking Process;
:Case Documentation;
stop
